92
00:06:07,580 --> 00:06:08,780
Can I meet with him to discuss?

93
00:06:08,950 --> 00:06:10,660
I can elaborate on our ideas.

94
00:06:12,160 --> 00:06:13,460
He's abroad right now.

95
00:06:14,390 --> 00:06:14,980
Don't worry.

96
00:06:15,000 --> 00:06:15,700
When he's back,

97
00:06:15,950 --> 00:06:16,930
I'll arrange a meeting, okay?

98
00:06:17,870 --> 00:06:19,370
Please make sure to tell this person

99
00:06:19,390 --> 00:06:20,930
we'll prioritize paying his share

100
00:06:20,950 --> 00:06:21,700
of the annual profits.

101
00:06:22,720 --> 00:06:23,170
No problem.

102
00:06:24,390 --> 00:06:25,660
Thank you, Shuhan!

103
00:06:27,630 --> 00:06:29,140
Is our startup funding

104
00:06:32,310 --> 00:06:33,850
hush money from Gao Hui?

105
00:06:36,830 --> 00:06:37,930
All these years I thought...

106
00:06:39,480 --> 00:06:40,700
I thought I owed you.

107
00:06:42,600 --> 00:06:43,660
I thought it was because of me

108
00:06:45,120 --> 00:06:46,460
