112
00:07:22,000 --> 00:07:23,290
Wang Shuhan, I truly never imagined.

113
00:07:25,630 --> 00:07:26,930
After all our years of friendship,

114
00:07:29,390 --> 00:07:30,370
you could do something like this.

115
00:07:33,560 --> 00:07:34,140
Not just that.

116
00:07:34,600 --> 00:07:35,660
I wanted to tell you.

117
00:07:37,360 --> 00:07:37,900
I wanted you to know

118
00:07:37,920 --> 00:07:38,700
that all these years,

119
00:07:39,950 --> 00:07:40,810
my understanding

120
00:07:41,510 --> 00:07:42,810
and sympathy for you were genuine.

121
00:07:45,160 --> 00:07:46,850
But my jealousy was real too.

122
00:07:49,270 --> 00:07:50,540
All these years, through everything,

123
00:07:51,920 --> 00:07:53,810
it never once crossed your mind
that it could be me.

124
00:07:53,830 --> 00:07:54,660
Why?

125
00:07:57,560 --> 00:07:58,170
Because in your eyes,

126
00:07:58,190 --> 00:07:59,290
I was never even worthy
of consideration.

127
00:08:00,950 --> 00:08:02,220
What are you?

128
00:08:03,830 --> 00:08:04,700
A ballet prodigy.

129
00:08:05,680 --> 00:08:06,780
With a bright future ahead.

130
00:08:07,360 --> 00:08:07,930
And me?

131
00:08:08,310 --> 00:08:09,100
Just a fishmonger.

132
00:08:09,430 --> 00:08:10,410
An ordinary person

133
00:08:10,600 --> 00:08:11,980
who did ballet for two years
before dropping out to work.

134
00:08:12,800 --> 00:08:13,370
All these years,

135
00:08:13,390 --> 00:08:14,780
you never once thought it could be me.

136
00:08:15,630 --> 00:08:16,370
Because you never

137
00:08:16,390 --> 00:08:18,140
saw me as someone on your level.

138
00:08:18,160 --> 00:08:19,250
That's what

139
00:08:19,270 --> 00:08:20,780
I hate the most!

140
00:08:21,040 --> 00:08:22,100
It's not that it never crossed my mind!

141
00:08:26,950 --> 00:08:28,370
I just didn't want to believe

142
00:08:29,740 --> 00:08:31,140
my best friend,

143
00:08:31,140 --> 00:08:31,580
you,

144
00:08:33,340 --> 00:08:34,940
could do such a thing.

145
00:08:43,220 --> 00:08:44,260
Best friend?

146
00:08:45,700 --> 00:08:47,460
I was just your perfect foil.

147
00:08:50,060 --> 00:08:50,460
Feng Rui,

148
00:08:51,140 --> 00:08:51,900
