163
00:09:23,820 --> 00:09:24,500
Who?

164
00:09:25,980 --> 00:09:27,140
I'm not sure yet.

165
00:09:27,140 --> 00:09:27,780
Just

166
00:09:28,540 --> 00:09:29,380
