170
00:09:46,940 --> 00:09:47,380
Ms. Tan.

171
00:09:49,180 --> 00:09:49,740
Thanks.

172
00:09:49,740 --> 00:09:50,180
Appreciate it.

173
00:09:50,700 --> 00:09:51,100
Shuhan.

174
00:09:53,420 --> 00:09:54,180
Why are you still here?

175
00:09:54,980 --> 00:09:55,460
Are...

176
00:09:57,620 --> 00:09:58,340
Are you both

177
00:09:58,740 --> 00:10:00,420
