178
00:10:01,340 --> 00:10:01,980
I'll pass.

179
00:10:01,980 --> 00:10:02,820
Too tired today.

180
00:10:02,820 --> 00:10:03,940
Just want to go back and rest.

181
00:10:04,820 --> 00:10:05,700
Maybe

182
00:10:05,900 --> 00:10:06,660
you two should go.

183
00:10:08,180 --> 00:10:09,060
Well, next time then.

184
00:10:10,420 --> 00:10:10,820
Okay.

185
00:10:11,460 --> 00:10:12,020
Next time.

186
00:10:12,580 --> 00:10:13,220
Definitely next time.

187
00:10:13,620 --> 00:10:13,900
Alright.

188
00:10:14,620 --> 00:10:14,940
Let's go.

189
00:10:15,740 --> 00:10:16,180
We're off.

190
00:10:16,180 --> 00:10:16,940
Bye.

191
00:10:17,220 --> 00:10:17,500
Bye.

192
00:10:27,340 --> 00:10:27,700
Feng Rui,

193
00:10:28,060 --> 00:10:29,100
