194
00:10:33,460 --> 00:10:34,100
Shoulders down.

195
00:10:35,620 --> 00:10:36,580
Eyes forward.

196
00:10:50,620 --> 00:10:51,700
Stop coming here.

197
00:10:52,340 --> 00:10:53,220
She's not coming back.

198
00:10:55,460 --> 00:10:56,060
Where is she?

199
00:10:58,740 --> 00:11:00,140
I really don't know.

200
00:11:00,260 --> 00:11:00,980
After she went to France,

201
00:11:00,980 --> 00:11:02,500
