202
00:11:04,780 --> 00:11:05,460
You're her best friend.

203
00:11:05,460 --> 00:11:06,740
You must know where she is.

204
00:11:07,980 --> 00:11:08,860
Why won't you tell me?

205
00:11:10,300 --> 00:11:11,940
I really don't know.

206
00:11:13,180 --> 00:11:14,140
Just go back.

207
00:11:18,100 --> 00:11:19,300
If you won't tell me,
don't bother stopping me.

208
00:11:50,900 --> 00:11:51,940
Don't tell her it was me.

209
00:11:54,500 --> 00:11:55,460
Whether you find her or not

210
00:11:56,180 --> 00:11:56,900
is up to you.

211
00:12:05,820 --> 00:12:06,580
Excuse me.

212
00:12:07,260 --> 00:12:08,620
Does Ms. Tan live here?

213
00:12:09,780 --> 00:12:12,780
I don't know the person you mentioned.

214
00:12:28,100 --> 00:12:28,900
Found her?

215
00:12:30,060 --> 00:12:30,420
No.

216
00:12:31,700 --> 00:12:32,460
Did you give up?

217
00:12:34,020 --> 00:12:36,020
Come back once you gave up.

218
00:12:37,380 --> 00:12:38,380
The company needs you.

219
00:12:46,220 --> 00:12:47,700
She's your best friend.

220
00:12:48,900 --> 00:12:50,140
Is this right for you to do that?

221
00:12:54,940 --> 00:12:56,140
Let me ask you,

222
00:12:58,020 --> 00:12:59,740
without Gao Hui's money,

223
00:12:59,740 --> 00:13:00,740
would you still do this?

224
00:13:01,020 --> 00:13:01,420
Yes.

225
00:13:05,980 --> 00:13:06,700
Why wouldn't I?

226
00:13:09,860 --> 00:13:10,260
You know what?

227
00:13:10,260 --> 00:13:11,340
There's one thing I still don't get.

228
00:13:12,100 --> 00:13:12,700
It's been

229
00:13:12,700 --> 00:13:13,580
so many years.

230
00:13:13,820 --> 00:13:14,860
Why are Yuan

231
00:13:15,820 --> 00:13:16,380
and Feng Rui

232
00:13:18,740 --> 00:13:19,900
still so into you?

233
00:13:21,500 --> 00:13:22,940
Guys like them

234
00:13:23,660 --> 00:13:24,940
could get any woman they want.

235
00:13:25,860 --> 00:13:26,980
So why you?

236
00:13:27,940 --> 00:13:29,660
What is it about you

237
00:13:29,860 --> 00:13:30,460
that draws them in,

238
00:13:30,460 --> 00:13:31,060
Tan Siting?

239
00:13:32,420 --> 00:13:35,140
How come you have both love
and a great career,

240
00:13:36,060 --> 00:13:37,580
and I've got nothing?

241
00:13:39,420 --> 00:13:41,540
So I was the one who brought down

242
00:13:41,540 --> 00:13:43,060
the perfect woman.

243
00:13:43,340 --> 00:13:44,980
Thinking about it,
I feel pretty accomplished.

244
00:13:52,540 --> 00:13:52,980
You know what?

245
00:13:52,980 --> 00:13:54,580
You're just making yourself
look pathetic.

246
00:13:55,020 --> 00:13:56,060
I'm not pathetic.

247
00:14:02,500 --> 00:14:04,140
Sitting at my computer

248
00:14:04,700 --> 00:14:05,900
and destroying you

249
00:14:06,780 --> 00:14:08,460
was the highlight

250
00:14:08,460 --> 00:14:09,820
of my life.

251
00:14:13,340 --> 00:14:14,940
You're not destroying anyone

252
00:14:15,980 --> 00:14:17,300
but yourself.

253
00:14:21,660 --> 00:14:23,660
Everyone faces setbacks in life.

254
00:14:25,940 --> 00:14:27,340
No one sails through smoothly.

255
00:14:28,940 --> 00:14:30,540
But you can't just fall apart like this.

256
00:14:32,060 --> 00:14:32,380
Right?

257
00:14:32,940 --> 00:14:33,860
Save your empty words.

258
00:14:33,860 --> 00:14:34,980
Tan Siting, just admit it.

259
00:14:35,140 --> 00:14:36,260
Admit you hate me.

260
00:14:36,260 --> 00:14:37,940
Admit you'll never forgive what I did.

261
00:14:38,020 --> 00:14:38,500
Admit...

262
00:14:38,500 --> 00:14:39,100
I don't!

263
00:14:40,260 --> 00:14:40,860
I don't hate you.

264
00:14:48,340 --> 00:14:49,220
I want to tell you,

265
00:14:54,220 --> 00:14:55,460
the Wang Shuhan I liked most

266
00:14:59,820 --> 00:15:01,340
was the one at the fish stall.

267
00:15:03,580 --> 00:15:04,220
She was so strong

268
00:15:04,220 --> 00:15:05,060
and full of light.

269
00:15:05,060 --> 00:15:05,580
Always

270
00:15:06,260 --> 00:15:07,140
smiling.

271
00:15:07,140 --> 00:15:08,780
She could

272
00:15:08,780 --> 00:15:09,740
handle anything.

273
00:15:11,380 --> 00:15:12,500
You think what you did

274
00:15:13,380 --> 00:15:14,380
would ruin me?

275
00:15:16,740 --> 00:15:17,820
You're hurting your own brother.

276
00:15:18,180 --> 00:15:20,700
♪Wanting to reach
that far-off horizon's line♪

277
00:15:20,900 --> 00:15:22,900
You hurt Yuan, not me!

278
00:15:24,860 --> 00:15:26,220
The one you love most!

279
00:15:34,940 --> 00:15:37,780
♪Many things aren't
as complex as they seem♪

280
00:15:38,020 --> 00:15:38,700
[Liu's Fresh Meat]
Really fresh.

281
00:15:38,700 --> 00:15:39,500
Let me introduce you.

282
00:15:39,500 --> 00:15:40,500
This is my daughter.

283
00:15:40,700 --> 00:15:41,860
Hello.

284
00:15:44,100 --> 00:15:45,020
You're meeting for the first time.

285
00:15:45,020 --> 00:15:45,620
Yeah.

286
00:15:45,780 --> 00:15:46,660
She's always busy with school.

287
00:15:46,660 --> 00:15:48,020
She only comes back a few times a month.

288
00:15:49,260 --> 00:15:50,460
Such a pretty girl.

289
00:15:50,700 --> 00:15:51,700
You're so lucky.

290
00:15:52,500 --> 00:15:53,780
She studies dance, right?

291
00:15:53,780 --> 00:15:54,420
Yes.

292
00:15:54,420 --> 00:15:56,980
Your daughter has grown
into such a graceful young lady.

293
00:15:59,020 --> 00:16:00,180
She just likes dancing a bit.

294
